name: HealthPharmaRx.com
overview:
HealthPhramaRx is a worldwide online pharmacy recommendation service based in Switzerland.

The company’s priority is to aid customers in saving money on well known brand name prescription medicinal drugs and to furnish them with highly result oriented and ideal health care details. By enjoying the convenience of your home you can access our online service setup and facilitate with quick and trouble-free service.

The medicines they offer are made in amenities that have been sanctioned by all of the subsequent authoritarian bodies:

* Food and Drug Administration (FDA), USA
* Medicines Control Agency (MCA), UK
* World Health Organization (WHO)
* Medicines Control Council (MCC), South Africa
* National Institute of Pharmacy (NIP), Hungary
* Pharmaceutical Inspection Convention (PIC), Germany
* Therapeutic Goods Administration (TGA), Australia
